snippet.title: Ghosts'n Demons trailer
snippet.description:
Celebrating Ghosts'n Goblins 30th years anniversary.

You can download game here:
https://bonusjz.itch.io/ghostsn-demons

Enjoy
Wanna give something for this ones that decided to help and donated
- they can get latest update with all improvements . If you cannot donate i have little challenge for you instead - make video or stream highlight of you beating at least level 2 boss on normal with 1 credit , post it in comments and  you get the game key.
